**UPDATED 11/27 @ 9pm**

Looking to sell what's left of these lower grade T206s.  Right now, I don't want to sell individually and would prefer to sell groupings.  I'd like to help out those set builders out there.  Nearly 200 available.  

Cards are priced below.  Accepting offers.  More cards = more of a deal. :)

Buy 5 or more, get 10% off.
Buy 10 or more, get 15% off.
Buy 20 or more, get 20% off.

Shipping for less than 10 cards will be $3.  Free shipping on 10+.
PM please.
PP F&F or add 3%.

For prices and pictures:

[URL="http://t206.weebly.com"]LINK #1[/URL]

[URL="http://www.collectorfocus.com/collection/jp1216/for-sale-or-trade"]LINK #2[/URL]
